<div class="page box sd">

<h2>Academic Commons Author Agreement</h2>

<P>
This form is for Columbia undergraduate and Master's students who are depositing a thesis in Academic Commons. If you have questions about the thesis deposit process, contact your department. If you want to know more about Academic Commons, please visit our  <a href="../deposit">self-deposit form</a>. If you want to know more about Academic Commons, please visit our <a href="http://support.academiccommons.columbia.edu/knowledgebase">FAQ</a> or contact us at cuac@libraries.cul.columbia.edu.	
</P>



<%= form_tag({ :action=>'submit_student_agreement'}, :method=>'post', :id=>'sd-form', :class=>'self-deposit-form', :charset=>'utf-8') do %>
<fieldset>

